{
  "stem": "8786.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Gunskirchen is a short but very sad story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said before, I think that the camp didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think, according to the records, out of 21,000 people, about 9,000 survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Daily, 400 to 500 people died, mostly fall asleep or typhus or from-- I was one of the-- I don't know why, but I did survive it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Much better than me-- many, many more better and stronger than me couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As I said, the food was just plain not around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were going out to wait for a little water and prayed for a little rain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I did see-- I did see a few of my close friends fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mentioned that before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember, also, that every-- the Friday night before the liberation, I was-- they asked me to daven.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was doing the prayers for a whole group of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Among the people, there were some actors from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They tried to entertain the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's no food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There's no sleeping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So at least these people should be credited for what they did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some actors-- I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were singing over their beautiful melodies-- and try to act and cheer up these terrible people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And as I mentioned it, the physical-- the physical condition was nothing to talk about.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But mentally, we were so dehumanized, like worms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this, this is what I-- hurts me to think of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is the worst part of, of what I can think of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because before, they did what they did to us physically, hurting us and beating us and starving us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were dehumanizing us.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
